  SCIENCE FACTS
============================================================

Domain:  Chemistry
Topic:   Conservation of Mass
Formula: Reactants mass = Products mass
Note:    Mass is conserved in all chemical reactions

Domain:  Medicine
Topic:   Blood Types
Formula: ABO system + Rh factor
Note:    Determines blood transfusion compatibility

Domain:  Physics
Topic:   Gravitational Force
Formula: F = Gm1m2/r²
Note:    Universal gravitation between all masses

Domain:  Biology
Topic:   Natural Selection
Formula: Favorable traits lead to greater reproduction
Note:    Mechanism of evolution; Darwin 1859

Domain:  Physics
Topic:   Ohm's Law
Formula: V = IR
Note:    Voltage, current, resistance relationship in circuits

============================================================
  ECONOMICS
============================================================

Concept:    Game Theory
Category:   Economics
Definition: Study of strategic interactions between rational agents
Formula:    Nash equilibrium
Economist:  John Nash
Example:    OPEC cartel coordination; nuclear deterrence strategy

Concept:    Keynesian Economics
Category:   Macroeconomics
Definition: Government fiscal policy stabilizes economy in recessions
Formula:    AD = C + I + G + NX
Economist:  John Maynard Keynes
Example:    2009 US stimulus; 2020-2021 COVID relief spending

Concept:    Inflation
Category:   Macroeconomics
Definition: General rise in price levels eroding purchasing power
Formula:    Inflation = (CPI_t - CPI_t-1)/CPI_t-1 x 100
Economist:  Irving Fisher
Example:    2022 US inflation hit 9.1%; Fed raised rates to combat it

